\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Are you a widower?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Widower. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 The year of your marriage please?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Date of the marriage? The year. 1907.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 The year of your birth?
