\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Who fed them when they were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Well I was the youngest - I don't remember much about it. I remember the high chair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
