\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 If you had any worries could you share them with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh aye, you could te
ll your mother - tell your mother anything. I remember coming home one day from school, our old schoolmaster he was a villain, an old Irish fellow name O'Neill. And we hadn't to go to school without a coat on. Well I - I was always a bit of a rebel in a w
ay and I was the school - schoolmasters errand boy, I used to take his notes to his home in Lower Broughton - used to go for the cane for him - when I brought it he'd give me the cane.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 For - something I'd done. He - he thought it was a joke but this 
day that I went - day something like today I well remember - like from memory - and - kept hitting me on the arm without coat on. Well there was wheals on. Well when I went home my mother said what's that? Oh, I said, nothing. She said, your father's got 
t
o see that. All right. So I had to show father. So - he said you'd better go to school and find out what it's all about - not having him hit like that for nothing. So - that was the sort of thing like. So me mother, she had to obey orders too. So Mr O'Nei
l
l come to the door. Everybody thought a lot of me mother including Mr O'Neill. Said William there's things that you shouldn't do, said, and - any way I told him not to come without a coat on - he come without a coat so he had to be chastised. So she she s
aid well it seems rather severe. Took my arm - when she went back and told him I got another tap with a shoe for doing wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Off your dad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Yes. Yes. He give me a bit more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Could you talk to your dad at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 No. You couldn't reason wit
h him. I - I never attempted it - I give him up early. Mind you, I wasn't against him but he - he was utterly impossible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 How did they expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh he expected you to do - he expected you to obey look never mind his order.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 What about your mother - how did she expect you to behave towards her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 
She - oh - she had to do what he said and that's what - I looked on it because he was nasty with me mother because he couldn't get his own way with me kind of and if I did
n't let him have his own way - nasty with her until I said you finish. Any more you go - I'm not keeping you no longer - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Did you have to behave in a certain way towards your mother?
