\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 How did they bring you up to behave towards each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh, we had to behave well to each other. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Suppose someone hit you did they tell you to hit back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh if anybody hit me I had to hit 'em back - I hadn't to let anyb
ody hit me. That was a strict order. I had to hit 'em because they used to hit me for going to Broughton. All - I survive with a black eye and I used to fight at school and all. The - the police knew all about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Well I - I think they were determined that we grew up to be all right - like the family. Those that lived and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 What did they think was right and what was wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 No, you hadn't to do wrong. You had to do everything that was right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 What did they think was right and what did they think was wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 
Well, they - they thought what was right what was right, they didn't think anything wrong that was wrong was right - they decided on the right thing
 in their own way. They weren't educated but they know right from wrong and they expected you to do it. And you grew up that you wanted to do it and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 What did they say was right though and what did they say was wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Well the right thing - the
y never said anything that was wrong was right. If - if you - I said anything wrong they'd say no, that's wrong. Oh, they - they wouldn't allow you to do anything wrong.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh, we hadn't to sear - he swore but you 
hadn't to swear - ooh, oh, I didn't - I never swore much in my life. I don't believe in it much - I don't think it does any good. I - I - I'm not saying I haven't done - in the Army or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 In home? I talked whether I was allowed or not. I - I was a bit combative.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 When you did anything that your parents didn't like how were you punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh well - I don't know there's anything - we didn't do anything that wasn't right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Your dad used to hit you with a shoe you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Did your mother ever hit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh but - I never knew me mother to strike one of us. She used to hug us not strike us.
