No, I don't - no, I don't - he never give me good hiding like continuous - it's - oh no, he never did that. He - he didn't - you couldn't call him a brutal father in the way of abuse but he was severe what bit he did that you kept out of
 it. And when I was - grown up like and - became a young man I wouldn't have none of it whereas when - I was president - it was only a small union - I was president of my union when I was twenty-two and I was errand boy for him for going for free beer for
 him at the same time and let him get away}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14040315\charrsid6767433  with it and - shop delegate I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
