t him get away with it and - I said your finished. I told - I told him, I said, you telling me what to do and I told him what I had accomplished at my age - said you've not accomplis
hed nothing, not a heap - a bit brutal - with him, I said and I'm not going to read for you, I said, and Janeys not going to read for you. But she used to do when I was out. But -
