\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 No, they - he - he - they were in that house when they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15881451 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433  and they were in that house when they died there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 You never thought he was afraid of who he should vote for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 
No, no they were in - as I say - they were in that house until they died. No, I don't think it interfered with - I don't think it entered into it the same as it does today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 When your parents weren't doing their work do you know how they spent - their leisure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Well - I - I - I can't remember them - me mother always seemed to be busy doing something if she wasn't cooking she was mending something.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 What about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh he did nothing. Only sat there and give orders. He worked very hard - it was a very hard job I believe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 She used to go one picnic. She had some friends - shopkeepers - and - there was one lady that kept a public house.
 Well she wasn't a drinker my mother but they used to go to the public house to have a talk and I used to go for her - to bring her home at night but - I think on one occasion the - the friends came to - this - I can remember one bit about this - came to 
o
ur house and one lady - they knew me father was a funny character - she wanted to sit on his knee. He'd have none of it. No. And she was a grand person - Mrs Walker - they had a tobacconist. Mrs Lee she had a tripe shop and Mrs Boughton they had this old 
fashioned pub. And they were friends like the - they used to go on a picnic occasionally, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 That's all your mother did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh she used to go on a picnic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 How many evenings a week did your father stay in?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Stay in? He never went out of he house from coming home on Saturday to going to work on Monday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Didn't he go to a club or a pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 He never went anywhere - never went in a pub. And yet he - he - we used to have to bring his drink - when he was on the beers he us
ed to ramble about a bit - I don't know where he went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 He never went to sports or races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Never went on a racecourse. I don't think he ever had a bet in his life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Did they belong to any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Savings clubs or boot clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Only his trade union. They used to come and collect that. He didn't of to the club for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Did he belong to a sick club or a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14040315\charrsid6767433 Foresters}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 . He belonged to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14040315\charrsid6767433 Foresters}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 . Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 That was a savings club was it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 No, it 
wasn't a club - they only used to go and pay their - money. And when he retired and run through his sick pay they gave him four shillings and he had that for himself - that was his spending money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Did they join a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 They was in funeral club - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh, I got on very well with them.
