 much. I used to fall out with him a bit about it. He'd a big family - eight girls and one lad and the lad was called after me and he died. Now he used to support Salford }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16152710\charrsid6767433 R}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 ugby team.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Who did you play with as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 And he - he used to go all over the place with 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Did you play with your brothers or your sisters or neighbours?
