rds became a - a sergeant in the Marines but - I skint him at this tipping so he hit me. So I belted him, oh, I didn't half belt Tommy and - he wasn't as heavy as me and I wasn't so heavy and - his mother was - oh, she was supposed to be a character. Iris
h
 blaggard she was. And she come up to our house and our Liza was - she was ill and she was sat near the door and - your Willie hit our Kom. She said, have you? I said, yes, and I'll hit him again and all if he hits me. Did he hit you? I said, yes, he did.
 So she said, clear off missus. She says I know all about you - I've heard all about you being a blaggard she said, clear off - we don't want you being a blaggard. I said - she said, I'll telling you if your son hits him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 You weren't allowed to play with him afterwards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 Oh - yes, we were pals - we were all right after. But - she was all right with me and all after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 But they never stopped you playing with any children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 She said - No, particular pals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15272546 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 You weren't ever stopped from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4413851 WF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10761150\charrsid6767433 
